data.description: As you walk into this spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home, you are greeted by an open floor plan with soaring ceilings and crown molding. The kitchen offers granite countertops and an abundance of counterspace, making it the perfect place to cook and entertain. The dining/eating area is open to the kitchen and living room, making it easy to interact with guests while preparing meals. The primary bedroom is set off with an en-suite bathroom containing a place to relax in a soaking tub, providing the perfect oasis to unwind after a long day. The home also has an abundance of storage throughout, including an oversized laundry room that offers additional space for storage.Outback, you will find an extended patio and large fenced in green area to enjoy, making it the perfect place to relax, play, or entertain guests.
